<div class="span12">
  <h3>Specific Organization</h3>
</div>

<div class="span8">
<pre>
[GET] /api/v1/organizations/:organization_id.json
</pre>

<h4>Parameters</h4>

<p>
  <code>organization_id</code> (required) the identifier for the organization
</p>

<p>
  <code>page</code> (optional) each page will return up to 30 reviews [default = page 1]
</p>

<h5>Example</h5>

<pre>
http://revtilt.com/api/v1/organizations/309.json?page=1
</pre>

<h4>Payload Schema</h4>

<pre>
{
  "conditionId": 0,
  "organization": {
    "name": "Imotion",
